SUMMARY:KHTA ANNUAL MEETING 
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\n3/29/202
 5\nMORGAN-MONROE S.F.\nFIRE HQ: Training Center\n\nMEETING 11 AM: Year Rev
 iew + meet your fellow members + informal talk with speaker + trail talk.\
 nLUNCH Noon\; pitch-in\; main dish\, drinks\, utensils provided.\nPROGRAM 
 1 PM: Speakers: TBD\, Nina Andrew\, loop trail in MMSF\nHIKE: Following th
 e meeting. Maybe.\n\nWebsite [www.knobstonehikingtrail.org](http://www.kno
 bstonehikingtrail.org)\nGmail: khtassociation@gmail.com\nFacebook Page [ww
 w.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100077384836069](http://www.facebook.com/pro
 file.php?id=100077384836069)\nFacebook Group [www.facebook.com/groups/2255
 586117953484](http://www.facebook.com/groups/2255586117953484)\nE-newslett
 er Substack [https://khta.substack.com/](https://khta.substack.com/)
