DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T130000
SUMMARY:Hike of the Tecumseh Trail extension as a
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\nCome hik
 e the just built section of the Tecumseh Trail extension. The Trail is lin
 ear but we can use forest roads to make it a loop. The gate at Hatfield Ri
 dge Road should be open so we’ll meet at the parking lot at the end of t
 he road. If people want\, we can go to lunch at Indy’s nearby when we ge
 t done. This is a beautiful section of trail so be sure to come.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of
 -indiana-meetup/events/314127595/
